org.smpp.smscsim

Interface PDUProcessorFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimulatorPDUProcessorFactory

    public interface PDUProcessorFactory
    Descandants of this class are passed to SMSCListener for generating instancies of classes derived from PDUProcessor. User should set up their derived classes so that they contain all information necessary for generating new PDU processors. This way is the logic of the PDU processing isolated from logic of establishing new connections (sessions).
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.1 $
    Author:
    Logica Mobile Networks SMPP Open Source Team
    See Also:
    PDUProcessor, SMSCListener, SMSCSession
